ba_tycoon_jail_v2

Map contains a multilevel cellblock With guard tower in the middle. 
Office area.
Vaultroom/gunroom
Cafe area
Yard with soccor field.
Church.
Libary.
Medical room.
Small storage Room
A set of control doors to decide where the mass of T's can go (cafe or outside)
A escape cell for T's

This was going to be called ba_space_escape
The out side area where the hole in the ground is, was to lead to a tele to a space-station with a win condition area/trigger for the T's. I will make that map later. For now its just a normal jail map.

Enjoy
